HEADWORD: Yedding
<hw>Yed"ding</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>geddung</ets>, <ets>gidding</ets>, <ets>giedding</ets>, from
<ets>gieddian</ets>, <ets>giddian</ets>, to sing, speak.]</ety> <def>The
song of a minstrel; hence, any song.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
